         MACRO
&NAME    $SW31
         GBLC  &ADRMODE
         AIF   ('&ADRMODE' EQ '24').GO24
         LCLC  &IDX
&IDX     SETC  '&SYSNDX'
* MACRO TO SWITCH TO 31 BIT AGAIN
&NAME    LA    R15,LA&IDX           ------->
         O     R15,=A(X'80000000')  ×SWITCH TO 31 BIT MODE
         $BSM  0,R15                ------->
LA&IDX   DS    0H
.GO24    ANOP
         MEND
